    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>ginger</strong> <strong>paste </strong>and <strong>tomatoes</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min further or until the tomatoes start to break down</p><p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p>",
