    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> tomato paste</strong> and <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Once the tomatoes have started to break down, add the <strong>coconut stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min further until thickened slightly</p><p>Once thickened, add the <strong>cooked salmon </strong>to the pan, and spoon the sauce over – this is your <strong>salmon & tomato curry</strong></p>",
