    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fluff the <strong>cooked rice </strong>with a fork, add a knob of <strong>butter</strong>, the <strong>chopped dill </strong>and season generously with <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>dill rice</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>salmon & tomato curry</strong> over the <strong>dill rice</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
